    Parameters

    • friendlyName
      String
      String

      Friendly name of the container.

    • backupManagementType
      Nullable<BackupManagementType>
      Nullable(Of BackupManagementType)

      Type of backup managemenent for the container. Possible values include: 'Invalid', 'AzureIaasVM', 'MAB', 'DPM', 'AzureBackupServer', 'AzureSql'

    • registrationStatus
      String
      String

      Status of registration of the container with the Recovery Services Vault.

    • healthStatus
      String
      String

      Status of health of the container.

    • containerType
      String
      String

      Type of the container. The value of this property for: 1. Compute Azure VM is Microsoft.Compute/virtualMachines 2. Classic Compute Azure VM is Microsoft.ClassicCompute/virtualMachines 3. Windows machines (like MAB, DPM etc) is Windows 4. Azure SQL instance is AzureSqlContainer.

    • canReRegister
      Nullable<Boolean>
      Nullable(Of Boolean)

      Can the container be registered one more time.

    • containerId
      Nullable<Int64>
      Nullable(Of Int64)

      ContainerID represents the container.

    • protectedItemCount
      Nullable<Int64>
      Nullable(Of Int64)

      Number of items backed up in this container.

    • agentVersion
      String
      String

      Agent version of this container.

    • extendedInfo
      MabContainerExtendedInfo
      MabContainerExtendedInfo

      Additional information for this container
